                        SCHEDULE ‘B’
                    </h3>
                          <p style="font-size:15px;text-align:justify;">{!Booking__c.UDS__c} Sq.ft of  undivided share right title and interest in Schedule  A Property and Apartment No. {!Booking__c.Unit_NumberFor__c}, {!Booking__c.BHK_Type__c} in {!Booking__c.Floor__c} floor {!Booking__c.Block_Number__c} block, having carpet area {!Booking__c.Carpet_Area__c} Sq.ft and Balcony Area of {!Booking__c.Balcony_Area__c} Sq.ft and super built up area of {!Booking__c.Built_up_area__c} Sq.ft along with {!Booking__c.Parking__c} parking slot in the building named as “{!Booking__c.Project__c}”</p>
                          <p style="font-size:15px;">IN WITNESS WHEREOF the parties herein have herein unto set their hands for this MOU 
                              on the day, month and year first above mentioned before the following witnesses: </p>
